在使用 `Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoad` 或 `Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom` 时,遇到错误:

```
Cannot resolve dependency to assembly 'Cognex.VisionPro, Version=53.2.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=ef0f902af9dee505'
because it has not been preloaded. When using the ReflectionOnly APIs, dependent assemblies must be pre-loaded or
loaded on demand through the ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve event.
```

## 根本原因

ReflectionOnly 加载上下文与正常加载上下文是隔离的:
- 依赖程序集不会自动加载
- 必须手动预加载或通过 `ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve` 事件处理
- 无法使用 `Assembly.Load`,必须使用 `Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoad*` 系列方法

## 解决方案

### 方案 1: 使用 ReflectionOnlyLoader 类(推荐)

```csharp
using (var loader = new ReflectionOnlyLoader())
{
    // 添加 Cognex.VisionPro 安装路径
    loader.AddProbingPath(@"C:\Program Files\Cognex\VisionPro");
    loader.AddProbingPath(@"C:\Program Files (x86)\Cognex\VisionPro");

    // 添加应用程序目录
    loader.AddProbingPath(AppDomain.CurrentDomain.BaseDirectory);

    // 预加载您的程序集(会自动处理所有依赖)
    Assembly assembly = loader.PreloadAssembly(@"YourAssembly.dll");

    // 现在可以安全使用反射
    Type[] types = assembly.GetTypes();
}
```

### 方案 2: 手动订阅 ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve 事件

```csharp
AppDomain.CurrentDomain.ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve += (sender, args) =>
{
    AssemblyName name = new AssemblyName(args.Name);

    // 处理 Cognex.VisionPro
    if (name.Name == "Cognex.VisionPro")
    {
        string cognexPath = @"C:\Program Files\Cognex\VisionPro\Cognex.VisionPro.dll";
        if (File.Exists(cognexPath))
        {
            return Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(cognexPath);
        }
    }

    // 尝试从 GAC 加载
    try
    {
        return Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoad(args.Name);
    }
    catch
    {
        // 尝试从本地路径加载
        string localPath = Path.Combine(
            AppDomain.CurrentDomain.BaseDirectory,
            name.Name + ".dll"
        );

        if (File.Exists(localPath))
        {
            return Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(localPath);
        }
    }

    return null;
};
```

### 方案 3: 显式预加载所有依赖

```csharp
// 在加载主程序集之前,先预加载 Cognex.VisionPro
string cognexPath = @"C:\Program Files\Cognex\VisionPro\Cognex.VisionPro.dll";
Assembly cognexAssembly = Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(cognexPath);

// 递归预加载 Cognex.VisionPro 的依赖项
foreach (AssemblyName refAsm in cognexAssembly.GetReferencedAssemblies())
{
    try
    {
        Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoad(refAsm.FullName);
    }
    catch
    {
        // 处理加载失败
    }
}

// 现在可以加载您的程序集
Assembly yourAssembly = Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(@"YourAssembly.dll");
```

## 关键注意事项

### 1. 路径配置

确保添加所有可能的 Cognex.VisionPro 安装路径:

```csharp
// 常见安装路径
var cognexPaths = new[]
{
    @"C:\Program Files\Cognex\VisionPro",
    @"C:\Program Files (x86)\Cognex\VisionPro",
    Path.Combine(Environment.GetFolderPath(Environment.SpecialFolder.ProgramFiles), "Cognex", "VisionPro"),
    Path.Combine(Environment.GetFolderPath(Environment.SpecialFolder.ProgramFilesX86), "Cognex", "VisionPro")
};

foreach (var path in cognexPaths.Where(Directory.Exists))
{
    loader.AddProbingPath(path);
}
```

### 2. 版本匹配

如果遇到版本不匹配,可以在 App.config 中配置绑定重定向:

```xml
<dependentAssembly>
  <assemblyIdentity name="Cognex.VisionPro"
                    publicKeyToken="ef0f902af9dee505" />
  <bindingRedirect oldVersion="0.0.0.0-65535.65535.65535.65535"
                   newVersion="53.2.0.0" />
</dependentAssembly>
```

### 3. 强名称验证

Cognex.VisionPro 是强名称程序集 (PublicKeyToken=ef0f902af9dee505),确保:
- 使用正确版本
- 程序集文件未被修改
- 从官方安装路径加载

### 4. 递归依赖

Cognex.VisionPro 可能依赖其他程序集,需要递归处理:

```csharp
void PreloadWithDependencies(string assemblyPath)
{
    var assembly = Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(assemblyPath);

    foreach (var refAsm in assembly.GetReferencedAssemblies())
    {
        try
        {
            // 尝试加载依赖项
            Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoad(refAsm.FullName);
        }
        catch
        {
            // 从本地路径尝试加载
            string depPath = Path.Combine(
                Path.GetDirectoryName(assemblyPath),
                refAsm.Name + ".dll"
            );

            if (File.Exists(depPath))
            {
                PreloadWithDependencies(depPath);
            }
        }
    }
}
```

## 调试技巧

### 启用程序集绑定日志

在 App.config 中启用:

```xml
<configuration>
  <runtime>
    <assemblyBinding xmlns="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:asm.v1">
      <dependentAssembly>
        <assemblyIdentity name="Cognex.VisionPro" />
      </dependentAssembly>
    </assemblyBinding>
  </runtime>

  <system.diagnostics>
    <sources>
      <source name="System.Reflection" switchValue="Verbose">
        <listeners>
          <add name="console" />
        </listeners>
      </source>
    </sources>
    <sharedListeners>
      <add name="console" type="System.Diagnostics.ConsoleTraceListener" />
    </sharedListeners>
  </system.diagnostics>
</configuration>
```

