## 📋 问题概述

**错误信息:**
```
Cannot resolve dependency to assembly 'Cognex.VisionPro, Version=53.2.0.0,
Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=ef0f902af9dee505' because it has not been
preloaded. When using the ReflectionOnly APIs, dependent assemblies must be
pre-loaded or loaded on demand through the ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve event.
```

**原因:** ReflectionOnly 加载上下文不会自动加载依赖程序集,需要手动处理。

---

## ⚡ 快速解决方案 (5分钟)

### 方案 A: 最小化代码(推荐快速修复)

将以下代码添加到您程序的开始处:

```csharp
// 在 Main 方法的第一行添加
AppDomain.CurrentDomain.ReflectionOnlyAssemblyResolve += (sender, args) =>
{
    AssemblyName name = new AssemblyName(args.Name);

    // 处理 Cognex.VisionPro
    if (name.Name == "Cognex.VisionPro")
    {
        string path = @"C:\Program Files\Cognex\VisionPro\Cognex.VisionPro.dll";
        if (File.Exists(path))
            return Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(path);
    }

    // 尝试从 GAC 加载
    try { return Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoad(args.Name); }
    catch { }

    // 尝试从本地加载
    string localPath = Path.Combine(AppDomain.CurrentDomain.BaseDirectory, name.Name + ".dll");
    if (File.Exists(localPath))
        return Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom(localPath);

    return null;
};

// 现在可以安全使用 ReflectionOnly 加载
Assembly asm = Assembly.ReflectionOnlyLoadFrom("YourAssembly.dll");
```

